  "title": "fix(insights): remove bindEvent",
  "body": "bindEvent is no longer handled in the component since #6403 (https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/6403/files#diff-e7717d55fdbbc94c7dd996f78b6f0f860332545d6fa8f6b843c940798334532cL94), so it's removed in this PR.\r\n\r\n[FX-3191]\r\n\r\nBREAKING CHANGE: the `bindEvent` related functions are non longer usable, use `sendEvent` instead\r\n\n\n[FX-3191]: https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/FX-3191?atlOrigin=eyJpIjoiNWRkNTljNzYxNjVmNDY3MDlhMDU5Y2ZhYzA5YTRkZjUiLCJwIjoiZ2l0aHViLWNvbS1KU1cifQ",
